## Bridge dev server
PORT=7777
ALLOWED_DEV_ORIGINS=

## Telegram notifier
##
## Configured via the bridge UI now (writes to ~/.claude/bridge.json
## under the `telegram` key — same per-machine file the apps roster
## lives in). The env vars below are kept ONLY as a fallback for
## installs that haven't migrated yet; new operators should ignore them
## and use the UI's "Telegram settings" panel instead.
##
##   1. Talk to @BotFather → /newbot, copy the token
##   2. Add the bot to your chat / group, then call
##      https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates and copy the
##      `chat.id` of the message you sent
##   3. Paste both into the bridge UI (Apps page → Telegram settings)
# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
# TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=
